## Proposed Changes

### Database Layer

#### [MODIFY] [ReminderDao.kt](file:///c:/Users/Kshitij%20Sharma/Desktop/Omnis/Magnum%20Opus/Personal%20Manager/app/src/main/java/com/productivity/app/data/dao/ReminderDao.kt)
Make `getPendingReminders` robust to correctly retrieve and reschedule reminders that are snoozed, even if their initial `datetime` has passed.

- Update the query:
  ```kotlin
  @Query("SELECT * FROM reminder WHERE is_completed = 0 AND (datetime > :now OR (is_snoozed = 1 AND snooze_until > :now)) ORDER BY datetime ASC")
  suspend fun getPendingReminders(now: Long): List<Reminder>
  ```

---

### Service Layer

#### [MODIFY] [NotificationHelper.kt](file:///c:/Users/Kshitij%20Sharma/Desktop/Omnis/Magnum%20Opus/Personal%20Manager/app/src/main/java/com/productivity/app/service/NotificationHelper.kt)
- Update notification channel IDs from `channel_*` to `channel_*_v2` to force channel recreation.
- Set the alarm ringtone sound (`RingtoneManager.getDefaultUri(RingtoneManager.TYPE_ALARM)`) and vibration pattern for high-importance channels (`Medicine`, `Meeting`, `Deadline`).
- Set the default notification sound (`RingtoneManager.getDefaultUri(RingtoneManager.TYPE_NOTIFICATION)`) for default-importance channels (`Travel`, `General`).

